        <updateDate>2011-06-23T15:31:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Home Office Deduction Simplification Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a taxpayer who uses a residence to conduct a trade or business a standard tax deduction equal to the lesser of $1,500 or the taxpayer's gross trade or business income derived from the business use of such residence.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
